title: CFB Slate 9 Slate
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco return to give you another week of picks. We started from scratch and Rico decided one by one who was allowed in the studio, burner accounts were brought into question, Big Cat recaps the devastating Wisconsin loss, and Dave hopes to improve his mortal lock record!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
